high_descs: Take left, walk to design on floor
Take right, go to table, grab yellow-handled knife
Take left, go to door, take right
Cut lettuce in half, cut one half in to six slices
Turn in a complete circle near door
Put knife down on to table next to white table
Walk back to lettuce
Take end lettuce slice in hand
Turn left, left again,, walk to table
Place slice on plate which is on black dining table
Pick up the plate with lettuce
Turn around, walk to black table
Set plate with lettuce down on black table
anns.task_desc: Slice lettuce, place on plate on small table.

high_descs: Turn left then right to face the table in front of you.
Take the knife from the table in front of you
Turn left then right to face the table with the lettuce in front of you.
Slice the lettuce on the table in front of you.
Turn around in a circle and face the black table.
Place the knife on the black table in front of you.
Turn right then face the table to your left.
Take a slice of lettuce from the table in front of you.
Turn around a head towards the black circle table in front of you.
Place the lettuce slice on the plate on the black table.
Pick up the plate with the lettuce slice from the black table in front of you.
Turn around and head towards the black square table in front of you.
Place the plate with the lettuce on the black table in front of you.
anns.task_desc: Put a plate with a lettuce slice on a black square table.

high_descs: Walk over to the white table.
Pick up the sharp knife on the table.
Walk to the other end of the white table to the head of lettuce.
Slice the lettuce next to the spatula.
Go to the end table to the left.
Set down the sharp knife on the end table.
Go back to the sliced lettuce on the end of the white table.
Pick up a slice of lettuce.
Take the slice to the round table in the corner across the room.
Set the lettuce on the square plate.
Pick up the plate with the lettuce on it.
Go to the end table at the end of the white table.
Set the plate with lettuce down on the end table.
anns.task_desc: Put plate with lettuce on the end table.

high_descs: Turn to your left and walk to the front of the white table.
Pick up the knife with the yellow handle located to the back right of the head of lettuce.
Turn to your left and walk to the other end of the white table where there is a second head of lettuce.
Slice the second head of lettuce into sections.
Make one full counterclockwise rotation.
Place the knife on the black table to the left of the white table with the blade facing the wall to the left.
Turn to stand at the sliced head of lettuce on the white table.
Pick up the right end slice of the head of lettuce.
Turn to your left and walk towards the door, hang a left and walk to the gray tray on the round black table.
Place the slice of lettuce on the gray tray.
Pick up the tray on the table.
Turn around and walk to the small black table with the knife with the yellow handle on it.
Place the tray behind the knife directly behind the yellow handle.
anns.task_desc: Place a lettuce slice on a tray on the small black table
